        <p>Microvista Technologies will refund your full amount only if Microvista Technologies agree on your cancelation request.</p>
        <p>To request a refund, simply contact us with your purchase details within ninety (90) days of your purchase. Please include your order number (sent to you via email after ordering) and optionally tell us why you’re requesting a refund – we take customer feedback very seriously and use it to constantly improve our products and quality of service. Refunds are being processed within 21 days period.</p>
